metadata.name: ur-ra
metadata.description:
ur-ra; is a fictional realm, known as the realm of lights.
inhabited by gods, goddesses, artificial intelligent robots, trojans, hackers, and many other wild things.
so beautiful and bright it birthed rumors that, you could see the light rays from deep space.

technologically advanced, known to be ran on fish economy, and having many portals.
portals built by the gods for many reasons, one being the most important of course, but, thatâ€™s a story for another day.

ur-ra is a state of mind, and the birth place of our story.

this piece was created to give you just a little idea as it fuels your imagination, enabling you to wander far and near, imagining, and visualizing what this beautiful realm looks like, or what life in it could be like.

as you begin to see right through this realm remember that all of that beauty and glory are not without a price, for this realm have a terrible curse!.

art is an experience, feel and enjoy it!.
